results.lead_paragraph: Clary Anderson is predictable. All the Montclair State football coach does is win, and then win some more. For 31 seasons, Anderson has not had a losing record and never had to revert to that old standby, "Wait 'til next year." This last season Anderson proved he was human after all and lost four of 10 games. Not even that had happened before.
